Developing
----------

Install dependencies using pip:

```bash
pip install -e .[develop]
```

Or using [poetry](https://python-poetry.org/docs/):

```bash
poetry install -E develop
```

Run databases:

```bash
docker-compose up -d
```

Run tests:

```bash
pytest tests -v -s
```


